## Session folder convention

```
{{SESSIONS_DIR}}/
├── {topic}.md                  # single-session topics (flat)
└── {project}/
    ├── MASTER.md               # always-loaded compressed permanent knowledge
    ├── 01-{slug}.md            # chronological session logs (changelog)
    ├── 02-{slug}.md
    └── ...
```

Iron rule: session-state lives ONLY in `{{SESSIONS_DIR}}/`. Never in domain folders. Working files (transcripts, code, assets) stay in their project folder. Session-state does not.

